                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>A steamer carrying A.H.H. Stuart's son B. Baldwin exploded; he is reported
                    to be okay.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/rvapr59.html#4.30e</note>
